<body>
	<!-- fullpop :: 매장 정보 -->
	<div id="pop01" class="fullPop">
		<h1>매장 정보</h1>
		<div class="popCon">
			<div class="storeDetail line">
				<div class="detName">
					<em class="brand">GS THE FRESH</em>
					<h2 class="name">역삼혜성점</h2>
					<!-- 20191211 수정 -->
					<div class="favor">
						<button type="button" class="edit star" aria-pressed="false">단골매장</button><!-- 설정시 aria-pressed="true" -->
						<button type="button" class="edit" aria-pressed="false">다른매장</button><!-- 설정시 aria-pressed="true" -->
					</div>
					<!-- //20191211 수정 -->
					<p class="desc">단골매장을 등록하시면, 단골매장의 행사상품, 사전예약, 앱주문현관결제 서비스를 이용하실 수 있습니다.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="detData">
					<ul class="infoData">
						<li><strong>영업시간</strong><span>10:00 ~ 22:00</span></li>
						<li><strong>매장주소</strong><span>서울 강남구 선릉로 221 상가 1층(도곡동, 도곡렉슬아파트)</span></li>
						<li><strong>대표번호</strong><span><a href="tel:02-2138-7162" class="txtLink">02-2138-7162</a></span></li>
						<li><strong>이번달 휴무일</strong><span>14일, 28일</span></li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="detServ">
					<!-- 20191224 수정 -->
					<ul class="infoService">
						<li role="text"><span class="icon"><img src="../../image/tmp/img_store_service.png" alt=""></span><span class="name">CAFE25</span></li>
						<li role="text"><span class="icon"><img src="../../image/tmp/img_store_service.png" alt=""></span><span class="name">베이커리</span></li>
						<li role="text"><span class="icon"><img src="../../image/tmp/img_store_service.png" alt=""></span><span class="name">택배</span></li>
						<li role="text"><span class="icon"><img src="../../image/tmp/img_store_service.png" alt=""></span><span class="name">알뜰마트</span></li>
						<li role="text"><span class="icon"><img src="../../image/tmp/img_store_service.png" alt=""></span><span class="name">조리식품</span></li>
						<li role="text"><span class="icon"><img src="../../image/tmp/img_store_service.png" alt=""></span><span class="name">영업중</span></li>
						<li role="text"><span class="icon"><img src="../../image/tmp/img_store_service.png" alt=""></span><span class="name">셀프계산대</span></li>
						<li role="text"><span class="icon"><img src="../../image/tmp/img_store_service.png" alt=""></span><span class="name">배달서비스</span></li>
					</ul>
					<!-- //20191224 수정 -->
				</div>
				<div class="detMap">
					<div class="mapBox">
						<div class="pinStore pinFR">GS THE FRESH</div>
